      • fields

        public static BigQuery.JobListOption fields(BigQuery.JobField... fields)
        Returns an option to specify the job's fields to be returned by the RPC call. If this option is not provided all job's fields are returned. JobOption.fields() can be used to specify only the fields of interest. JobInfo.jobId(), JobStatus.state(), JobStatus.error() as well as type-specific configuration (e.g. QueryJobInfo.query() for Query Jobs) are always returned, even if not specified. BigQuery.JobField.SELF_LINK and BigQuery.JobField.ETAG can not be selected when listing jobs.
